{"tid":2039020,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"推文被Twitter標記為「事實錯誤」川普指其扼殺言論自由及影響大選 將嚴管或關閉社交平台","createTime":"2020-05-27T22:24:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T22:10:01.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8425a67c000595025e8656b5c5c5bbeb3991faf7","tid":2039020,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T22:24:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imageproxy.themaven.net/https%3A%2F%2Fimages.saymedia-content.com%2F.image%2FMTcyODM0MjQzODg4NTU1NzA2%2Ftwitter-corrects-trump-tweets.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimageproxy.themaven.net%2Fhttps%253A%252F%252Fimages.saymedia-content.com%252F.image%252FMTcyODM0MjQzODg4NTU1NzA2%252Ftwitter-corrects-trump-tweets.png&h=51509b6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2020/05/27/13/28881830-8361491-Donald_Trump_warned_Wednesday_morning_that_his_administration-a-7_1590583104394.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2020%2F05%2F27%2F13%2F28881830-8361491-Donald_Trump_warned_Wednesday_morning_that_his_administration-a-7_1590583104394.jpg&h=132323f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2020-05-27 20:58:56<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國總統川普是推特（Twitter）活躍用戶，26日傳出川普2則貼文被推特官方標記「事實錯誤」的標籤，成為該社交媒體平台的首例；對此，川普除稍早痛斥推特扼殺言論自由外，今（27）日晚間再嗆聲若不改善，將考慮強力管制或關閉社交媒體平台。<br />\n<br />\n據貼文內容，川普今（27）日針對自己的貼文遭到推特標記「不實」指出，共和黨認為各大社交媒體平台開始箝制保守派的聲音，若狀態沒有改善，不排除將強力管制或關閉社交媒體平台。<br />\n<br />\n川普指出，2016年這些平台也做過一樣的事情但是失敗了，他不會容許這種變本加厲的情況再次發生，正如他絕不會讓大選以郵寄的方式進行，「那只會變成作弊、偽造、盜竊選票的『吃到飽』自助餐」，讓最擅長作弊的人勝出。最後，川普疾聲呼籲社交媒體公司即刻進行改善。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，川普在美國當地時間26日晚間針對大選「郵寄選票」發表質疑和看法，被推特官方標記驚嘆號並顯示「取得關於郵寄選票的事實真相」，等於指控川普言論並非事實。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3179363\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3179363&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5PuNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=2c969fd8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3179363&h=7a182edb\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3179363</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/2020/05/26/twitter-has-started-fact-checking-trump/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fpolitics%2F2020%2F05%2F26%2Ftwitter-has-started-fact-checking-trump%2F&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5PuNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=0ab328af\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/2020/05/26/twitter-has-started-fact-checking-trump/</a>"},{"pid":"d3518e08802cbfd80cece76232aff8945552f4cc","tid":2039020,"uid":183758,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T22:25:15.000Z","msg":"共諜李飛飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c175e8ee738987b5aa944a1f5fba6e85f7b67e7","tid":2039020,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T22:30:21.000Z","msg":"yt都係一批評中共就刪片，睇下佢幾時刪埋侵侵同pompeo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5611d0426ee88e1b89e8e934bdf211a9555513f0","tid":2039020,"uid":131875,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T21:18:40.000Z","msg":"終於twitter都玩埋黃標"},{"pid":"6a07de6c0e16f462c05fe21a9b18baad15542006","tid":2039020,"uid":321837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T22:10:01.000Z","msg":"本地左膠家下開始明麥卡錫係好人啦?<br />\n有麥卡錫，仲有咁多紅媒、偽人出嚟猖狂舔支咩"}]}